@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jpgtsu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.10 - v2 + 0.34) + (v2 + 0.71 + v1 + 0.71)))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.70) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.81)) / wp.cos(wp.sin(v0 + 0.38)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(v2) + 0.72)
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v1 + 0.63 + tmp + 0.67)))
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.10 / v1 + 0.17)) + 0.55)
    v2 = 0.99
    v2 = (v2 - wp.exp((tmp + 0.70 - tmp + 0.55)))
    data[tid] = v0
